latestPosts.caption:
Attempting my first knitted garment. Had to undo the whole thing twice but now another two day's worth of knitting and it'll be finished!! 

Mistake 1: Not making a proper gauge swatch and ending up piece that would have been way too big

Mistake 2: Joining the left and right sides but forgetting to untwist the work so I ended up with a mobius strip instead of a top.

latestPosts.caption:
Just me singin' in my vanity 🌻

Song is called 'Suzy Went to Space' and it's NOT on Spotify yet. It'll be part of my next album 'Sea Creature on the Sofa'. Until then, you can come listen to it at my next show at @gyltbangalore (ticket link in bio) ;) 

I wrote the song because I wanted to find a way to talk about the flow state I get into when I'm writing. It's like going to space. Magical, but also scientific.

Aaaaaand film number two commences! So happy to be on a film set once again, this time with @vineet.joshi_films and @mesunnysingh for @decibel_movie 🌻

Also I swear I didn't break the set lol
